  {
    icon: '⏰',
    title: 'Responds Outside Hours',
    text: "Customers text at all hours — early mornings, late evenings, weekends. The AI responds instantly, regardless of the time. That late-night text about a dripping tap gets acknowledged in seconds, not ignored until Monday."
  },
  {
    icon: '📋',
    title: 'Structured Lead Capture',
    text: "The AI doesn't just forward the raw text message to you. It reads the content, extracts the job type, location, and urgency, and sends you a structured lead with all the information organised and ready to action."
