  description="AI SMS responses for UK tradesmen. Instant professional text replies to customer enquiries. Captures lead details automatically. £19/month. No contracts."
  canonicalUrl="/ai-sms-for-tradesmen/"
  channelName="AI SMS"
  channelSlugPrefix="ai-sms"
  headline="Professional Text Replies to Every Customer Enquiry. Instantly."
  accentWord="Every Customer"
  subhead="When a potential customer texts your number about a leaking tap or a dodgy fuse board, they want to know you got the message. AI SMS responds immediately with a professional reply — even when you're elbow-deep in a job."
  speedStat="58% of UK consumers text businesses for service enquiries."
  speedText="Texting is quick, easy, and doesn't require the customer to stop what they're doing. They fire off a text and expect a response. If they don't hear back within the hour, they text the next tradesman on their list. AI SMS makes sure you respond first."
  scenario="It's Saturday morning. A homeowner in Leeds has noticed a damp patch forming above the bathroom extractor fan. She's found your number on a local directory and texts: 'Hi, I've got damp coming through above the bathroom fan. Can you come and have a look? I'm in LS8.' You're three hours into a loft conversion in Harrogate and won't check your phone until lunchtime. Without AI SMS, that text sits unread. She texts another roofer who responds in five minutes and books the inspection. With Rapid Receptionist, the AI replies immediately, captures her name, address, and the problem, and you get a structured lead notification you can action during your break."
